title: Impractical Jokers Cruise is no joke!
text:
Impractical Jokers take their witty hijinks to sea Impractical Jokers Cruise is no joke! Adv: 
Aug 05, 2015 Adv: 
ATLANTA, GA - The Impractical Jokers of truTV's hit show, are teaming up with Atlanta based Sixthman, the industry leader in festivals at sea, to bring their special brand of hijinks to life on a cruise. This four-night cruise, sailing on Norwegian Pearl from Miami to Cozumel, January 11-15, 2016, will feature comedians, live musical performances, and of course a heavy dose of the Jokers' antics. 
Sal, Joe, Q, and Murr will serve as honorary captains while hosting numerous onboard activities, participating in a Q&A, and performing a hilarious set in the ship's grand Stardust Theater. A handful of other acts including comedians, live bands, and DJs will round out this event.
